name: ONE Season 2 (Episodes 10-18)
description:
ONE: Season Two, alternatively known as ONE Season 2,[1][2] is the second and last season of ONE. Like the last season, this season also has 9 episodes. It primarily focuses on Liam's journey to find The Plane, and stopping Airy from continuing the competition for good. It officially finished on August 21st, 2022 with the last episode, "Self-Titled". On October 12, 2022, a 1 hour 14 minute compilation of all 9 episodes from the season was released on Cheesy Hfj's channel.
PLEASE WATCH HFJONE SEASON ONE BEFORE WATCHING THIS!!!!
